<!-- Game Cheats Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Play Phalanx -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>When the game is first loading up, hold Select and Start on controller 2. Play using controller 2.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Watch Mode -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Hold L1 + L2 + R1 + R2 and hold Down on the Controller. Choose ''Vs. Play'' and you will see the computer fight itself</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Zulu -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Defeat the game with every character on any difficulty setting</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock XTAL -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>To fight against XTAL, play all the way through the game with all eight characters, including ZULU, without using a continue</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock NECO -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>To fight against NECO, play the game using XTAL as your character and without using a continue. Then, hold L1+L2+R1+R2 then select then start</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Stage Select -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Play for more than 30 hours, then return to the title screen. You can now choose any stage</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Secret comic strip -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Beat the game on the Easy setting without using any continues. Then highlight the Option mode on the title screen and use your second controller and hold L1,L2,R1,R2,Start, and Select. Then you'll see the comic strip</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Infinite energy P1 -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80110764 00D0</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
       	</td>

     </tr>
</table>

